lead_paragraph: Olympic and world heptathlon champion Jessica Ennis-Hill is set to miss the indoor athletics season with an Achilles injury, disrupting her preparations for the defence of her title at the Rio Games in August.

headline.print_headline: Olympic Champion Ennis-Hill to Miss Indoor Season
